2113
01:47:44,782 --> 01:47:46,049
- No...
- Yes, God damn it!

2114
01:47:46,116 --> 01:47:47,184
Just tell me
what the hell is goin' on.

2115
01:47:47,251 --> 01:47:48,385
- No!
- Are you involved in this

2116
01:47:48,452 --> 01:47:49,720
- or not?
- No, that's not my father

