- No.

2149
01:49:00,257 --> 01:49:01,592
...so you could hide
behind her and Frank.

2150
01:49:01,658 --> 01:49:03,260
- That's not true.
- People are getting killed.

2151
01:49:03,327 --> 01:49:04,394
- You got it wrong.
- You got your own daughter's

2152
01:49:04,461 --> 01:49:05,929
- life at risk...
